g.text: Rabbit MQ (Message Queue for backGround Processing)
1. Pulls the data from the Queue
2. Fetch the Video from cloudfare r2
4. Upload these HLS Streams to the CloudFlare R2 Bucket.
5. Update the document in the Mongo (is_converted = True)
6. Publishes the message to the Redis Pub Sub
7. Clean removing video and hls streams from local consumer.
